org.yawlfoundation.yawl.util

Class AbstractEngineClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yawlfoundation.yawl.util.AbstractEngineClient
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EngineClient, InterfaceClients

    public abstract class AbstractEngineClient
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class that abstracts interface connections and calls between custom services and the Engine and other services as needed, besides those that go through InterfaceBWebsideController
    Author:
    Michael Adams
    Created/Last Date:
    05/01/2015
